{"tha-ap24:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap24:0.2":"Subhutivagga ","tha-ap24:0.3":"2 Upavanattheraapadana ","tha-ap24:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap24:1.2":"sabbadhammana paragu; ","tha-ap24:1.3":"Jalitva aggikkhandhova, ","tha-ap24:1.4":"sambuddho parinibbuto. ","tha-ap24:2.1":"Mahajana samagamma, ","tha-ap24:2.2":"pujayitva tathagatam; ","tha-ap24:2.3":"Citam katvana sukatam, ","tha-ap24:2.4":"sariram abhiropayum. ","tha-ap24:3.1":"Sarirakiccam katvana, ","tha-ap24:3.2":"dhatum tattha samanayum; ","tha-ap24:3.3":"Sadevamanusa sabbe, ","tha-ap24:3.4":"buddhathupam akamsu te. ","tha-ap24:4.1":"Pathama kancanamaya, ","tha-ap24:4.2":"dutiyasi manimaya; ","tha-ap24:4.3":"Tatiya rupiyamaya, ","tha-ap24:4.4":"catutthi phalikamaya. ","tha-ap24:5.1":"Tatha pancamiya bhumi, ","tha-ap24:5.2":"lohitangamaya ahu; ","tha-ap24:5.3":"Chattha masaragallassa, ","tha-ap24:5.4":"sabbaratanamayupari. ","tha-ap24:6.1":"Jangha manimaya asi, ","tha-ap24:6.2":"vedika ratanamaya; ","tha-ap24:6.3":"Sabbasonnamayo thupo, ","tha-ap24:6.4":"uddham yojanamuggato. ","tha-ap24:7.1":"Deva tattha samagantva, ","tha-ap24:7.2":"ekato mantayum tada; ","tha-ap24:7.3":"Mayampi thupam kassama, ","tha-ap24:7.4":"lokanathassa tadino. ","tha-ap24:8.1":"Dhatu avenika natthi, ","tha-ap24:8.2":"sariram ekapinditam; ","tha-ap24:8.3":"Imamhi buddhathupamhi, ","tha-ap24:8.4":"kassama kancukam mayam. ","tha-ap24:9.1":"Deva sattahi ratnehi, ","tha-ap24:9.2":"annam vaddhesu yojanam; ","tha-ap24:9.3":"Thupo dviyojanubbedho, ","tha-ap24:9.4":"timiram byapahanti so. ","tha-ap24:10.1":"Naga tattha samagantva, ","tha-ap24:10.2":"ekato mantayum tada; ","tha-ap24:10.3":"Manussa ceva deva ca, ","tha-ap24:10.4":"buddhathupam akamsu te. ","tha-ap24:11.1":"Ma no pamatta assumha, ","tha-ap24:11.2":"appamatta sadevaka; ","tha-ap24:11.3":"Mayampi thupam kassama, ","tha-ap24:11.4":"lokanathassa tadino. ","tha-ap24:12.1":"Indanilam mahanilam, ","tha-ap24:12.2":"atho jotirasam manim; ","tha-ap24:12.3":"Ekato sannipatetva, ","tha-ap24:12.4":"buddhathupam achadayum. ","tha-ap24:13.1":"Sabbam manimayam asi, ","tha-ap24:13.2":"tavata buddhacetiyam; ","tha-ap24:13.3":"Tiyojanasamubbiddham, ","tha-ap24:13.4":"alokakaranam tada. ","tha-ap24:14.1":"Garula ca samagantva, ","tha-ap24:14.2":"ekato mantayum tada; ","tha-ap24:14.3":"Manussa deva naga ca, ","tha-ap24:14.4":"buddhathupam akamsu te. ","tha-ap24:15.1":"‘Ma no pamatta assumha, ","tha-ap24:15.2":"appamatta sadevaka; ","tha-ap24:15.3":"Mayampi thupam kassama, ","tha-ap24:15.4":"lokanathassa tadino’. ","tha-ap24:16.1":"Sabbam manimayam thupam, ","tha-ap24:16.2":"akarum te ca kancukam; ","tha-ap24:16.3":"Yojanam tepi vaddhesum, ","tha-ap24:16.4":"ayatam buddhacetiyam. ","tha-ap24:17.1":"Catuyojanamubbiddho, ","tha-ap24:17.2":"buddhathupo virocati; ","tha-ap24:17.3":"Obhaseti disa sabba, ","tha-ap24:17.4":"sataramsiva uggato. ","tha-ap24:18.1":"Kumbhanda ca samagantva, ","tha-ap24:18.2":"ekato mantayum tada; ","tha-ap24:18.3":"Manussa ceva deva ca, ","tha-ap24:18.4":"naga ca garula tatha; ","tha-ap24:18.5":"Paccekam buddhasetthassa, ","tha-ap24:18.6":"akamsu thupamuttamam. ","tha-ap24:19.1":"‘Ma no pamatta assumha, ","tha-ap24:19.2":"appamatta sadevaka; ","tha-ap24:19.3":"Mayampi thupam kassama, ","tha-ap24:19.4":"lokanathassa tadino; ","tha-ap24:19.5":"Ratanehi chadessama, ","tha-ap24:19.6":"ayatam buddhacetiyam’. ","tha-ap24:20.1":"Yojanam tepi vaddhesum, ","tha-ap24:20.2":"ayatam buddhacetiyam; ","tha-ap24:20.3":"Pancayojanamubbiddho, ","tha-ap24:20.4":"thupo obhasate tada. ","tha-ap24:21.1":"Yakkha tattha samagantva, ","tha-ap24:21.2":"ekato mantayum tada; ","tha-ap24:21.3":"Manussa deva naga ca, ","tha-ap24:21.4":"garula kumbhaandaka. ","tha-ap24:22.1":"Paccekam buddhasetthassa, ","tha-ap24:22.2":"akamsu thupamuttamam; ","tha-ap24:22.3":"‘Ma no pamatta assumha, ","tha-ap24:22.4":"appamatta sadevaka. ","tha-ap24:23.1":"Mayampi thupam kassama, ","tha-ap24:23.2":"lokanathassa tadino; ","tha-ap24:23.3":"Phalikahi chadessama, ","tha-ap24:23.4":"ayatam buddhacetiyam’. ","tha-ap24:24.1":"Yojanam tepi vaddhesum, ","tha-ap24:24.2":"ayatam buddhacetiyam; ","tha-ap24:24.3":"Cha yojanani ubbiddho, ","tha-ap24:24.4":"thupo obhasate tada. ","tha-ap24:25.1":"Gandhabba ca samagantva, ","tha-ap24:25.2":"ekato mantayum tada; ","tha-ap24:25.3":"‘Manuja devata naga, ","tha-ap24:25.4":"garula kumbhayakkhaka. ","tha-ap24:26.1":"Sabbekamsu buddhathupam, ","tha-ap24:26.2":"mayamettha akaraka; ","tha-ap24:26.3":"Mayampi thupam kassama, ","tha-ap24:26.4":"lokanathassa tadino’. ","tha-ap24:27.1":"Vediyo satta katvana, ","tha-ap24:27.2":"chattamaropayimsu te; ","tha-ap24:27.3":"Sabbasonnamayam thupam, ","tha-ap24:27.4":"gandhabba karayum tada. ","tha-ap24:28.1":"Sattayojanamubbiddho, ","tha-ap24:28.2":"thupo obhasate tada; ","tha-ap24:28.3":"Rattindiva na nayanti, ","tha-ap24:28.4":"aloko hoti sabbada. ","tha-ap24:29.1":"Abhibhonti na tassabha, ","tha-ap24:29.2":"candasura sataraka; ","tha-ap24:29.3":"Samanta yojanasate, ","tha-ap24:29.4":"padipopi na pajjali. ","tha-ap24:30.1":"Tena kalena ye keci, ","tha-ap24:30.2":"thupam pujenti manusa; ","tha-ap24:30.3":"Na te thupamaruhanti, ","tha-ap24:30.4":"ambare ukkhipanti te. ","tha-ap24:31.1":"Devehi thapito yakkho, ","tha-ap24:31.2":"abhisammatanamako; ","tha-ap24:31.3":"Dhajam va pupphadamam va, ","tha-ap24:31.4":"abhiropeti uttari. ","tha-ap24:32.1":"Na te passanti tam yakkham, ","tha-ap24:32.2":"damam passanti gacchato; ","tha-ap24:32.3":"Evam passitva gacchanta, ","tha-ap24:32.4":"sabbe gacchanti suggatim. ","tha-ap24:33.1":"Viruddha ye pavacane, ","tha-ap24:33.2":"pasanna ye ca sasane; ","tha-ap24:33.3":"Patiheram datthukama, ","tha-ap24:33.4":"thupam pujenti manusa. ","tha-ap24:34.1":"Nagare hamsavatiya, ","tha-ap24:34.2":"ahosim bhatako tada; ","tha-ap24:34.3":"Amoditam janam disva, ","tha-ap24:34.4":"evam cintesaham tada. ","tha-ap24:35.1":"‘Ularo bhagava heso, ","tha-ap24:35.2":"yassa dhatudharedisam; ","tha-ap24:35.3":"Ima ca janata tuttha, ","tha-ap24:35.4":"karam kubbam na tappare. ","tha-ap24:36.1":"Ahampi karam kassami, ","tha-ap24:36.2":"lokanathassa tadino; ","tha-ap24:36.3":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap24:36.4":"bhavissami anagate’. ","tha-ap24:37.1":"Sudhotam rajakenaham, ","tha-ap24:37.2":"uttareyyapatam mama; ","tha-ap24:37.3":"Velagge alaggetvana, ","tha-ap24:37.4":"dhajam ukkhipimambare. ","tha-ap24:38.1":"Abhisammatako gayha, ","tha-ap24:38.2":"ambarehasi me dhajam; ","tha-ap24:38.3":"Vateritam dhajam disva, ","tha-ap24:38.4":"bhiyyo hasam janesaham. ","tha-ap24:39.1":"Tattha cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap24:39.2":"samanam upasankamim; ","tha-ap24:39.3":"Tam bhikkhum abhivadetva, ","tha-ap24:39.4":"vipakam pucchaham dhaje. ","tha-ap24:40.1":"So me kathesi ananda, ","tha-ap24:40.2":"pitisanjananam mama; ","tha-ap24:40.3":"‘Tassa dhajassa vipakam, ","tha-ap24:40.4":"anubhossasi sabbada. ","tha-ap24:41.1":"Hatthi assa ratha patti, ","tha-ap24:41.2":"sena ca caturangini; ","tha-ap24:41.3":"Parivaressanti tam niccam, ","tha-ap24:41.4":"dhajadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap24:42.1":"Satthituriyasahassani, ","tha-ap24:42.2":"bheriyo samalankata; ","tha-ap24:42.3":"Parivaressanti tam niccam, ","tha-ap24:42.4":"dhajadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap24:43.1":"Chalasitisahassani, ","tha-ap24:43.2":"nariyo samalankata; ","tha-ap24:43.3":"Vicittavatthabharana, ","tha-ap24:43.4":"amuttamanikundala. ","tha-ap24:44.1":"Alarapamha hasula, ","tha-ap24:44.2":"susanna tanumajjhima; ","tha-ap24:44.3":"Parivaressanti tam niccam, ","tha-ap24:44.4":"dhajadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap24:45.1":"Timsakappasahassani, ","tha-ap24:45.2":"devaloke ramissasi; ","tha-ap24:45.3":"Asitikkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap24:45.4":"devarajjam karissasi. ","tha-ap24:46.1":"Sahassakkhattum raja ca, ","tha-ap24:46.2":"cakkavatti bhavissasi; ","tha-ap24:46.3":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap24:46.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap24:47.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap24:47.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap24:47.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap24:47.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap24:48.1":"Devaloka cavitvana, ","tha-ap24:48.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap24:48.3":"Punnakammena samyutto, ","tha-ap24:48.4":"brahmabandhu bhavissasi. ","tha-ap24:49.1":"Asitikotim chaddetva, ","tha-ap24:49.2":"dase kammakare bahu; ","tha-ap24:49.3":"Gotamassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap24:49.4":"sasane pabbajissasi. ","tha-ap24:50.1":"Aradhayitva sambuddham, ","tha-ap24:50.2":"gotamam sakyapungavam; ","tha-ap24:50.3":"Upavanoti namena, ","tha-ap24:50.4":"hessasi satthu savako’. ","tha-ap24:51.1":"Satasahasse katam kammam, ","tha-ap24:51.2":"phalam dassesi me idha; ","tha-ap24:51.3":"Sumutto saravegova, ","tha-ap24:51.4":"kilese jhapayi mama. ","tha-ap24:52.1":"Cakkavattissa santassa, ","tha-ap24:52.2":"catudipissarassa me; ","tha-ap24:52.3":"Tiyojanani samanta, ","tha-ap24:52.4":"ussisanti dhaja sada. ","tha-ap24:53.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap24:53.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap24:53.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap24:53.4":"dhajadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap24:54.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap24:54.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap24:54.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap24:54.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap24:55.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma upavano thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap24:56.1":"Upavanattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}